<div class="space-y-12">

  <div class="max-w-3xl">
    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-5">The Planning and Community Development Department manages land use, zoning administration, building permits, code enforcement, and long-range planning for the City of Aberdeen.</p>
    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Walk-ins are welcome during business hours. Use the phone in the City Hall lobby and dial <strong>extension 221</strong> to speak with a planner before visiting.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-xl p-4 text-sm text-blue-800">
    <strong>Fee Update:</strong> New fee schedule effective January 1, 2025. <a href="https://www.harfordcountymd.gov/3806/Fee-Changes-Effective-112025" class="underline hover:no-underline font-semibold">View Harford County fee changes.</a>
  </div>

  <div>
